        public Set<ContextException> initialize(AModuleModules m,
                                        StateContext initialContext)
        Initialize the system for execution from this module. The initial Context is created, and populated with name/value pairs from the local definitions and the imported definitions. If state is defined by the module, this is also initialized, creating the state Context.
        Parameters:

        initialContext -
        Returns:
